  "description": "A ***lyric essay*** is a hybrid form that borrows techniques from [poetry](../../poetry/_index.md) — fragmentation, juxtaposition, white space, [imagery](../../../terms/imagery.md) over [argument](./argument.md) — to do the [essay](../../../terms/essay.md)'s work of thinking through a subject.",
